            "state": "translated",
            "value": "在 %@ 找不到二进制文件"
          }
        },
        "fr-FR": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Binaire introuvable à l'emplacement %@"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "auth.copilot.code-copied": {
      "comment": "Success message with copied GitHub auth code",
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "🌐 Browser opened for GitHub authentication.\\n\\n📋 Code copied to clipboard:\\n\\n%@\\n\\nJust paste it in the browser!\\n\\nThe app will automatically detect when you're authenticated."
          }
        },
        "es-419": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "🌐 Navegador abierto para autenticación de GitHub.\\n\\n📋 Código copiado al portapapeles:\\n\\n%@\\n\\n¡Solo pégalo en el navegador!\\n\\nLa aplicación detectará automáticamente cuando te hayas autenticado."
          }
        },
        "zh-CN": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "🌐 已打开浏览器进行 GitHub 身份验证。\n\n📋 代码已复制到剪贴板：\n\n%@\n\n只需在浏览器中粘贴即可！\n\n应用将自动检测您的身份验证状态。"
          }
        },
        "fr-FR": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "🌐 Navigateur ouvert pour l'authentification GitHub.\\n\\n📋 Code copié dans le presse-papiers :\\n\\n%@\\n\\nCollez-le simplement dans le navigateur !\\n\\nL'application détectera automatiquement lorsque vous serez authentifié."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "auth.copilot.check-browser": {
      "comment": "Fallback message when device code cannot be extracted",
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "🌐 Browser opened for GitHub authentication.\\n\\nCheck your terminal or the opened browser for the device code.\\n\\nThe app will automatically detect when you're authenticated."
          }
        },
        "es-419": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "🌐 Navegador abierto para autenticación de GitHub.\\n\\nRevisa tu terminal o el navegador abierto para ver el código del dispositivo.\\n\\nLa aplicación detectará automáticamente cuando te hayas autenticado."
          }
        },
        "zh-CN": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "🌐 已打开浏览器进行 GitHub 身份验证。\\n\\n请在终端或已打开的浏览器中查看设备代码。\\n\\n应用将在您完成身份验证后自动检测。"
          }
        },
        "fr-FR": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "🌐 Navigateur ouvert pour l'authentification GitHub.\\n\\nVérifiez votre terminal ou le navigateur ouvert pour le code de l'appareil.\\n\\nL'application détectera automatiquement lorsque vous serez authentifié."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "auth.browser-opened": {
      "comment": "Generic success message when auth browser opens",
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "🌐 Browser opened for authentication.\\n\\nPlease complete the login in your browser.\\n\\nThe app will automatically detect when you're authenticated."
          }
        },
        "es-419": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "🌐 Navegador abierto para autenticación.\\n\\nPor favor, completa el inicio de sesión en tu navegador.\\n\\nLa aplicación detectará automáticamente cuando hayas sido autenticado."
          }
        },
        "zh-CN": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "🌐 已打开浏览器进行身份验证。\\n\\n请在浏览器中完成登录。\\n\\n应用将自动检测您的登录状态。"
          }
        },
        "fr-FR": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "🌐 Navigateur ouvert pour l'authentification.\\n\\nVeuillez terminer la connexion dans votre navigateur.\\n\\nL'application détectera automatiquement votre authentification."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "auth.error.process-failed": {
      "comment": "Error when auth process fails without specific error message",
